Interface MultiValueFunction<O,A,I extends Iterable<A>>


  • public interface MultiValueFunction<O,A,I extends Iterable<A>>
    A functional interface which, when used with Java 8+, allows CQEngine attributes MultiValueAttribute and MultiValueNullableAttribute to be created from lambda expressions.
